commit.message: Fix bullets heading towards the top left corner
Fix a stupid build error slowing down development

Massive feature commit + refactoring
- Game now uses Phaser state system instead of our own implementation
- No more 1100ms delay on game load
- Game is hooked up to the back end
- Back end has primitive code for querying instance servers
UI starting to take shape, also was able to load resources
Fix Gulp production build not working due to a race condition
Fix assets not making it into the dist folder
Fix some stuff being hardcoded for development
Fix tab navigation not showing the correct active tab
Turn the header logo into a clickable link
